                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-498" type="given" value="ANN"></interp>ANN SMITH</persName>
                  </hi>. I am single. On the 7th of April, a little before nine o'clock in the evening, I was in Fenchurch-street, with Joseph Farrance, we got to the corner of Philpot-Iane, when the prisoner stepped forward, and snatched my reticule from my arm—it had a prayer-book and a hand-kerchief in it—these are mine—(<hi rend="italic">looking at them.</hi>)</p>
               <p>
