                        <interp inst="t18390408-name-499" type="given" value="JOSEPH"></interp>JOSEPH FARRANCE</persName>
                  </hi>. I am a watchmaker, and live in Bishopsgate-street. I was with Ann Smith, and saw the prisoner snatch the reticule from her—he ran down Philpot-lane—I pursued, and cried, "Stop thief"—he was taken by the policeman in a few minutes.</p>
